  "reference_number": "RUS3035",
  "remarks": "\nLeyla Rinatovna FAZLEEVA is an “involved person” under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulation 2019 in that she (1) is or has been responsible for, engaged in or provided support for policies or actions which undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, namely the Government of Russia’s programme for the forced deportation and re-education of Ukrainian children; and (2) is or has worked for or been affiliated to the Government of Russia in her role as the Deputy Prime Minister of the Republic of Tatarstan and Chairperson of the Republic’s Commission on Juvenile Affairs and the Protection of their Rights. \n",
